  [*Drache*], [*Il pleut des cordes*], [A heavy downpour or torrential rain. A very common word, given the Belgian weather! Example: "_Quelle drache aujourd'hui !_"],
  [*À tantôt*], [*À plus tard / À tout à l'heure*], ["See you later (today)." This is considered a bit old-fashioned in France but is very common and friendly in Belgium.],
